name: The mystery of the female world

metadata.name: Woman with a cigar.
metadata.description:
Woman with a cigar.

A painting inspired by a visit to Cuba.

 I saw this lady of the bar, she was free, relaxed and smoking a cigar. The whole world seemed to stop for a moment to admire her.... 

I enjoy every detail of my paintings. Each element born accidentally or deliberately fervently loved by me. This is the element I gave birth to in the morning and I was so happy about it, it brought almost the whole picture together, it became an eye-catcher 

7589x5047 Only NFT , 
Unfortunately Physical Art no longer exists
